# Ticket #1 – Account Lockout

## Issue:
The user is locked out of their account

## Investigation:
Opened Active Directory and Client Computer
Located the user account
Verified that the account is not disabled
Confirmed that the account is locked

## Root Cause:
The user exceeded the amount of failed login attempts and has been temporarily locked out of their account

## Resolution:
Unlocked the account
Had the user login and reset their password

## Verification:
User logged into the workstation successfully

## Lessons Learned:
Unlocking an account does not automatically reset the password
